I used to live on a loud busy street so I bought some earplugs off amazon to help me sleep better.  However, I accidentally bought a bulk box of about 500 of them. I hate returning stuff so I kept them and now I‚Äôm earplug wealthy.

Before long though...Honeysuckles stumbled upon one laying on the floor and it was love at first sight. Not sure why.  Again...maybe don't try this at home.  She mostly just likes tossing it around and we take it away before she starts eating it, but best not to take the chance. But do what you want, I'm not the doggy earplug police. 
Moral of the story...read your amazon descriptions more carefully or else you might make your best friend feel pure joy. (Also yes, that is a large light-up Prince symbol in the background )
